# Video ad factory rules

**Context:** `@docs/architecture_ledger.json` · `shared/types/campaign-v1.ts`

1. Cloud APIs only — ElevenLabs `eleven_multilingual_v2`, Fal queue endpoint.  
2. Use Zod types from `shared/types/campaign-v1.ts` for all campaign payloads.  
3. `rendering-bridge` is the only place to swap video vendors.  
4. Set `current_step` to `HUMAN_APPROVAL_REQUIRED` before final render dispatch.  
5. Never import from `apps/apple-store-api/`.
